cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.HC, cs.RO, cs.MM

The paper discusses the processing of high resolution video data and 3D model based tracking, which are both related to computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The topic of remote tower operations also involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the use of hardware for parallel computing suggests a potential connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
